r317 | sam | 2006-03-06 09:32:40 +0100 (Mon, 06 Mar 2006) | 9 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/caca-config.in
   M /trunk/configure.ac
   M /trunk/examples/aafire.c
   M /trunk/examples/cacaball.c
   M /trunk/examples/cacamoir.c
